          "ingredient_id": "5a97334e-92a0-4532-bc98-bb86ff529dd2",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "\u2022 1 gallon-sized plastic freezer bag"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "9bad3133-8c08-4b8c-9e75-5caeca1e70cd",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "\u2022 1 quart-sized plastic freezer bag (or two if you buy a 12oz can of milk)"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "d0729d3b-1e99-46e8-82a9-9594d4925116",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "PREP"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "7e6258b8-25a4-4ea8-8d58-4709fc6339fa",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "1. Label your freezer bag."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "31276e40-97fe-49f2-b62c-c7080328521f",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "2. To your gallon-sized freezer bag, add all ingredients (except evaporated milk and"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "c07d7738-6b35-4f26-9979-2c5b7c720393",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "chicken broth). To keep potatoes from browning, chop them last and add the to the"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "103ab82f-3670-4ed2-acb8-8512eb48377e",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "top of your freezer bag."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "9ef8f6f0-aa9a-43f0-9979-6878f0ea6a18",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "3. Add evaporated milk to a quart-sized plastic freezer bag. Seal, and add to gallonsized bag."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "932b4fae-79e3-4ad7-9384-5ab26348f8c0",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "4. Remove as much air from the gallon-sized freezer bag as possible, seal, and lay flat"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "cb5bb5b0-6a79-493b-b145-4ef131574f5a",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "in your freezer."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "db49eb15-f9db-4873-9f0d-e53fd492f1d9",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "COOK"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "7f52ef9e-9ac9-499c-aeb2-ee64ed9c5c36",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "1. The night before cooking, move frozen bag to your refrigerator to thaw."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "00488bb5-93a1-47ca-babe-9f615553c689",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "2. The morning of cooking, pour contents of gallon-sized freezer bag into your"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "da45e981-4690-4b7a-adfa-64a0a9abc325",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "crockpot and add chicken broth. Keep bag of evaporated milk in the refrigerator."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "ba82ad8c-230c-4067-b58b-2e446fc5d233",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "3. Cook item in crockpot on \u201clow\u201d setting for 8 hours, or until carrots and potatoes"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "3e6cdabb-8726-4cca-9147-e86bb0311f1b",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "are soft. Stir in evaporated milk and leave lid open a crack. Continue to cook 15"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "97544e69-fa41-451b-85d9-a619f956a9aa",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "minutes or until heated through."
        }
      ],
